<p><span class="anchor" id="p43"></span>فِي مُوضحَة الرَّأْس<a href="#p43" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p44"></span>وَمِنْهَا الْعظم خلف الْأذن<a href="#p44" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
